Node.Notes: Tree assumes with most: her branches become white, despite LXX making the enemies the subject. This verb in hiphil = become white.
Addressee uncertain. Could be land or vine and fig or Jerusalem personified as a woman like widespread personification of Jerusalem, Judah, and YHWH’s people in Jeremiah, Lamentations, and Isaiah.
Tree assumes: Wail like a virgin with sackcloth around her [wails] over the husband she was betrothed to.
Priests, ministers of the altar, and ministers of my God probably address the same referent group.
